original_title: World Series of Fighting 24: Fitch vs. Okami
overview: World Series of Fighting 24: Fitch vs. Okami was a mixed martial arts event held October 17, 2015 in Mashantucket, Connecticut, United States. This event aired live on NBCSN in the U.S and on Fight Network in Canada.
title: World Series of Fighting 24: Fitch vs. Okami
